OL,4,G1850FLocation, Location, Location
OL,5,     GIn Greater Manchester, Kirstie
OL,6,     GAllsopp helps Jacinta and Marco,
OL,7,     Gwho've outgrown their home. And
OL,8,     GPhil Spencer's with Olivia and
OL,9,     GAmy, who want to put down roots
OL,10,     Gin the north.
OL,11,G1955FPopMaster TV
OL,12,     GKen Bruce hosts the fourth heat,
OL,13,     Gbut who really knows the charts?
OL,14,     GOnly one player can secure their
OL,15,     Gplace to play 3 in 10. Will they
OL,16,     Gget a silver or a gold disc?
